****Understanding HTML Tables****
-->Tables are for DATA, not pictures or "table of contents"

****Defining HTML Tables****
-Caption
-Header
-Body
-Footer

<tr> - rows
    <th> - table header
    <td> - table data
colspan/rowspan - allows for the data cell to span over multiple colomns or rows


****Formatting Tables****
-->Use CSS to style Tables
    -Control spacing, borders, padding, etc.
